# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# walk — depth-first traversal applying before/after callbacks.
# Callbacks travel wrapped ([f/r]); vg-noarg / none means "no callback".
# Paths are fresh lists per visit (the canonical TS shares one mutable
# array per depth purely as an allocation optimisation).
