]]

# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# merge — deep merge of a list of values; later values win; the first
# element is modified in place. Ported over walk with an explicit state
# stack (cur/dst frames) instead of the canonical TS closures, so the
# walker callbacks stay capture-free (and merge stays re-entrant).
